<!-- ============ TESTIMONIALS ============ -->
<section class="svc-testimonials">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="svc-section-head reveal" style="--d:0">
      <h2 class="svc-title">What our clients say.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-testimonials__grid reveal" style="--d:80">
      <article class="t-card">
        <div class="t-quote-mark">"</div>
        <p class="t-quote">From the get-go it was really impressive how much knowledge Kristy has of the industry. It gave me a lot of confidence as we built the marketing plan for my business. It was finally something that was going to have an effect. I was throwing a lot of stuff out there and nothing was sticking. The plan and the support Kristy has given me has been fundamental to the growth of my business. We've started to gain exposure, in a short amount of time, we're starting to get new leads as a result. I couldn't have been happier with the whole process. MPIAD is a great price and high value. I loved it.</p>
        <div class="t-attr">
          <span class="t-name">Steven Kearney</span>
          <span class="t-role">Founder, Secure Minded</span>
          <span class="t-service">Marketing Plan in a Day</span>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="t-card">
        <div class="t-quote-mark">"</div>
        <p class="t-quote">I have worked with Kristy 1:1 on my business marketing. Kristy is a true advisor, provides great strategy (not just digital marketing), practical suggestions for action, and her genuine care and dedication to the future of my business and to raising my professional profile and personal brand is clear. I feel like she is in my corner and she supports me as a colleague and client. Thank you Kristy!</p>
        <div class="t-attr">
          <span class="t-name">Eleni Dracakis</span>
          <span class="t-role">Founder, Eleni Dracakis Business Psychologist</span>
          <span class="t-service">Marketing Plan in a Day</span>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ FAQ ============ -->
<div class="svc-wave">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 80" preserveAspectRatio="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
    <path d="M0,44 C320,80 800,6 1440,52 L1440,80 L0,80 Z" fill="#fff"/>
  </svg>
</div>
<section class="svc-faq">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="svc-faq__inner">
      <div class="reveal" style="--d:0">
        <h2 class="svc-title" style="margin-top:0">Before you book.</h2>
        <p class="section-intro" style="margin-top:24px">If you're weighing up whether we're the right fit, these are the questions we get asked most.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq__list reveal" style="--d:80">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-item__btn" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>What gets covered on the day?</span>
          <span class="faq-item__icon"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-item__panel"><div class="faq-item__panel-inner">The session covers everything you need to build a solid marketing foundation for your small business. That includes clarifying your target audience, defining your brand positioning, identifying the right marketing channels for your business, and mapping out a prioritised action plan you can implement straight away. Every session is tailored to your specific business and goals, so the day looks different for every client.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-item__btn" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>Do I need to prepare anything before the day?</span>
          <span class="faq-item__icon"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-item__panel"><div class="faq-item__panel-inner">Yes, and that's part of what makes it work. Before your session, you'll complete a short pre-work document and have a 30-minute strategy call with Kristy. This means the day itself is focused entirely on building your plan.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-item__btn" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>What do I walk away with?</span>
          <span class="faq-item__icon"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-item__panel"><div class="faq-item__panel-inner">A complete, tailored marketing plan you can start using immediately. Not a template with your name on it - a plan built specifically around your business, your goals, and your market.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-item__btn" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>What if I'm not based in Brisbane?</span>
          <span class="faq-item__icon"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-item__panel"><div class="faq-item__panel-inner">No problem. Sessions are available via Zoom, and if you'd prefer two shorter sessions instead of one full day, that can be arranged to suit your schedule and time zone.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-item__btn" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>I'm not a marketer. Will I be able to implement this myself?</span>
          <span class="faq-item__icon"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-item__panel"><div class="faq-item__panel-inner">That's exactly who this is designed for. The session is built around equipping you to run your own marketing with confidence - you don't need a background in marketing or a team behind you.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-item__btn" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>How far in advance do I need to book?</span>
          <span class="faq-item__icon"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-item__panel"><div class="faq-item__panel-inner">Only one spot is available per month, so availability is limited. Booking 4 to 6 weeks ahead is recommended, though it's worth reaching out to check current availability.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-item__btn" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>How do I book a Marketing Plan in a Day session?</span>
          <span class="faq-item__icon"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-item__panel"><div class="faq-item__panel-inner">Booking is straightforward. Click the link on this page to schedule a call with Kristy. Once confirmed, you'll receive an invoice for 50% upfront to secure your spot, with the remaining 50% due after your follow-up accountability call. From there, Kristy will book in your 30-minute strategy call where you'll talk through your business, your marketing goals, and any current challenges. You'll also receive your pre-work on this call, so you arrive on the day ready to hit the ground running. After that, your full-day session gets locked in and you're all set.</div></div>
      </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ FINAL CTA ============ -->
<section class="finalcta" id="book" data-screen-label="12 Final CTA" data-comment-anchor="finalcta">
